Asian School of Business , is a business school located in Trivandrum , Kerala in India . The school was established in 2005 . Its aim is to facilitate and promote studies & research with focus on professional education and its programme is called Post Graduation Programme in Management ( PGPM ) , in emerging areas of higher education in disciplines of marketing , finance , human resources , Systems and operations and so on . The admissions to these programmes are through a Common Entrance Test followed by GD and interview . The school is presently situated at Technopark in Kerala . It plans to shift to the new campus which is approximately 16 acres of land in size , with modern and top class facilities . Late Mr MNV Nair was the Professor Emeritus and Prof. S Jagadish was the first Director of the school . Kerala 's Asian School of Business set to open , Yahoo ! . 